@startuml
title Builder - Ejemplo 5 - Builder moderno sin Director para orden de compra
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class PurchaseOrder {
    +total(): double
    +describe(): String
    +builder(String buyer): Builder
  }
  class Builder {
    +addItem(String sku): Builder
    +discount(double discount): Builder
    +shippingMethod(String shippingMethod): Builder
    +build(): PurchaseOrder
  }
}

PurchaseOrder ..> Builder : crea
Builder ..> PurchaseOrder : crea
Main ..> PurchaseOrder : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
